defaultThe 
defaultBSNA 
defaultwelcomes the Health Select Committee’s inquiry into the management of long term conditions
default given their prevalence and significant impact on health service budgets in England
default. This response deals with the diagnosis and management of coeliac disease on the NHS
default. 
defaultWe would welcome the opportunity to discuss these issues with you in more detail and answer any questions you may have. 
